      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MONSOON ETHICS (2) was among the minors three back at Grafton then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 2 this time where he has won before. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Key player on best and worth another chance. MISS GLAMOURPUSS (1) has a strong record this trip with nine wins and four placings from 14 starts. Comes off a (22.29) win last time, scoring by 2 lengths in a NG over 400m at Bulli. Looks one of the chances. FEDERAL SNIPER (4) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. Comes off a (22.16) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a NG over 400m at this track. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SAMSON'S RIOT (7) is always a threat when he draws this box.",
